export interface IDeduction {
  id?: string,
  uploadedBy?: string,
  uploadedDt?: string,
  deductionType?: string,
  triggeredBy?: string,
  triggeredDt?: string,
  downloadedBy?: string,
  downloadedDt?: string,
  collectedCount?: number,
  collectedAmount?: number,
  status?: string,
  remarks?: string,
  remarksBy?: string,
  remarksDt?: string,
  uploadedFileId? : string,
  resultFileId? : string
}

export enum DeductionType {
  SAFRA = 'SAFRA',
  OTHERS = 'Others'
}
